Merle MOORE v. FISH ENGINEERING CORPORATION. No. 4946. United States Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. Nov. 2, 1954. Payne H. Ratner, Payne H. Ratner, Jr., and Keith Eales, Wichita, Kan., for appellant. Robert C. Foulston, and Malcolm Miller, Wichita, Kan., for appellee.
